{
  "2147530": {
    "name": "活魔人",
    "steam_appid": 2147530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/f57312417bc94ded343166787c21bad6.avif?t=1753897492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras_big/f57312417bc94ded343166787c21bad6.avif?t=1753897492 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在疯狂的战斗中对抗无情的恶魔大军，掌握超过 50 种独特武器 —— 包括火焰喷射器、手榴弹、元素武器和旋转机关枪 —— 在史诗般的战场上释放毁灭之力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有无限升级、深度伤害系统、独特角色，以及创建疯狂自定义构筑的能力，每一局都提供独特路线、爆炸性协同效果和近乎无限的可能性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/e5dd1e9425a4cb0a74c2c4db2850b48a.avif?t=1753897492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras_big/e5dd1e9425a4cb0a74c2c4db2850b48a.avif?t=1753897492 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越残酷的关卡，直面巨型 Boss，揭开连接天堂与地狱的秘密 —— 一个地狱无主、路西法失踪、神秘天使从阴影中现身并提供帮助的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场血腥的斗争中，唯有最强者才能生存。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/1cad5497484c3046f992926bc70799a5.avif?t=1753897492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras_big/1cad5497484c3046f992926bc70799a5.avif?t=1753897492 width=800 height=124 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用符文修改你的武器和技能，赋予其毁灭性效果，如多重射击、轨道刀刃、元素爆发等等。混合搭配符文，扩展你的武装，在战场上造成巨大破坏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/50c7768c37b8516a74b0f715c05560cb.poster.avif?t=1753897492\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/50c7768c37b8516a74b0f715c05560cb.webm?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/50c7768c37b8516a74b0f715c05560cb.mp4?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从五条独特的路径中选择 —— 时间、幸运、专注、力量与平衡 —— 并在同一路径中堆叠升级，解锁强大的协同效果，化身为自然的不可阻挡之力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/5cd2cd0fab7f3456b9516a2162de6611.avif?t=1753897492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras_big/5cd2cd0fab7f3456b9516a2162de6611.avif?t=1753897492 width=800 height=124 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 76 种以上独特的被动技能，自定义你的构筑。创造疯狂的组合，定义你自己的战斗风格 —— 从冷静的驱魔人到混乱的毁灭者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/1dfa7fcb9204934f5a2aa956f840faeb.poster.avif?t=1753897492\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/1dfa7fcb9204934f5a2aa956f840faeb.webm?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/1dfa7fcb9204934f5a2aa956f840faeb.mp4?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/e61cc8578986755d522dfcfdd29863ee.avif?t=1753897492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras_big/e61cc8578986755d522dfcfdd29863ee.avif?t=1753897492 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败地狱领主、堕落天使和天堂守护者，在残酷的战斗中将你的力量推向极限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/3bd2f700117639ea0e8cc44ac6ace276.poster.avif?t=1753897492\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/3bd2f700117639ea0e8cc44ac6ace276.webm?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/3bd2f700117639ea0e8cc44ac6ace276.mp4?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/6965e4f597164e3f50c71b4eeb289427.avif?t=1753897492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras_big/6965e4f597164e3f50c71b4eeb289427.avif?t=1753897492 width=800 height=124 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在混乱的战斗中掌控元素之力，每一种元素都扮演着至关重要的角色。系统遵循“剪刀石头布”的逻辑 —— 水克火，火引爆气体，电在潮湿环境中更加致命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/143bd32ed06163627937a117dec8cef3.poster.avif?t=1753897492\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/143bd32ed06163627937a117dec8cef3.webm?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/143bd32ed06163627937a117dec8cef3.mp4?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>毁灭性效果</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元素攻击会造成冻结、燃烧、流血和电击等残酷状态，极大地改变战斗节奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/a46894a111f5a92bbcb82e29561516f5.poster.avif?t=1753897492\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/a46894a111f5a92bbcb82e29561516f5.webm?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/a46894a111f5a92bbcb82e29561516f5.mp4?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>元素联动与适应型敌人</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元素之间会以强大而出人意料的方式相互反应 —— 火焰引燃、水熄灭、电在潮湿中传播等。这些联动可以彻底改变战斗局势。同时，敌人会根据当前状态动态变化，获得新的抗性和弱点。想要主宰战场，你必须观察局势、巧妙组合元素，并在敌人最脆弱时给予致命一击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/6b873ab56306a4f6b52934a118c5c6e5.avif?t=1753897492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras_big/6b873ab56306a4f6b52934a118c5c6e5.avif?t=1753897492 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
